title: Bush isna t picking sides in House GOP speaker fight
text:
Bush isna t picking sides in House GO... Bush isna t picking sides in House GOP speaker fight There are 3 comments on the The Washington Post story from 14 hrs ago, titled Bush isna t picking sides in House GOP speaker fight . In it, The Washington Post reports that: 
Jeb Bush says he isn't getting involved in the chaotic battle among House Republicans over who will be the next speaker because he's focused on shaking up the system from the outside. "What goes on in Washington, I follow it because it could be important but it really has nothing to do with my message for sure," Bush told reporters after a campaign event in New Hampshire on Wednesday. Join the discussion below, or Read more at The Washington Post.
